parameters: $gameVariables.setValue(21, "ErBaOp.How long is this going to take?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "MeBaEx.I only need to ask you a few questions. It won’t take long.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "ErWoOp.You’re right. She is a hard ass.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McAnOp.She doesn’t want to explore the Wilkes case any further.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "ErBaOp.What do you think? Do you think Madalyn just wanted money?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McBaDe.I don’t know. But I’d love to catch her.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "ErBaOp.Well… If I find anything more, I’ll let you know.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "ErAnDe.Spill it, 1Hero. I want to know everything.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "ErAnOp.Don’t give me that shit. Are you undercover? Are you working for that guild?...");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "ErAnEx.I don’t know… maybe Madalyn… maybe us.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "ErAnDe.What do you mean? Are you saying there is nothing between us?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McAnEx.I never said I wanted anything serious. Why are you acting like this?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McAnEx.You can trust me. I’ve not lied to you.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "ErAnDe.You’re fucking those girls who came to your house, aren’t you?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McAnOp.No!... Well, yes… Why do you care? I thought we were cool with that kind of thing.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "NeAnDe.I’ll tell you the same thing I told him. You’re making a mistake.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "ObBaEx^.Excuse me. But Miss Cole has been cleared to leave.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "NeFlEx.Any chance I can get the Goblet of Santo Morales back?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "ObAnOp^.Just be glad you’re not behind bars.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McWoCl.I don’t get it. How’d you pull this off?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "NeFlEx.Think about it. You’re a smart guy.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McSaOp^.I’m even more confused than before I talked to her.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "MeAnOp.What the hell? Get out of here!");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "DaBaEx.She’s already been cleared… We need to find Kimura.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McWoEx.David… Andrea is leaving the country. She’s the Guild’s leader now.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "DaBaEx.You’re free to go. Someone vouched for you.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "DaBaDe.Believe me… I’m as shocked as you are.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "DaAnDe.As long as I don’t have to.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "DaAnDe.Still trying to find Kimura? Good luck.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "AdBaOp.We have a lot to cover. I hope you’re ready to absorb everything before we have to meet at the Channel 4 skyrise.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "AdBaEx.As you already know, the Eclipse Guild is falling and soon they will be eradicated.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "AdBaOp.We’re up to 316 arrests now and suspect only a few dozen more stragglers are left.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McShOp.Wow. I’m surprised there is any threat at all if the numbers are that low.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "AdBaEx.There isn’t a threat. At least, not anymore.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "AdBaOp.Our undercover operations have eliminated most of the members, but that information has to remain between the two of us. ");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "AdAnOp.Don’t let it slip, 1Hero. We’re not ready to tell the public about our inside men.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "AdBaEx.It’s true that a majority of Guild operations have taken place in this state, but most arrests have been concentrated in the southern counties.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McBaDe.So we’re in the clear up here in the north?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "AdBaEx.We are now. But we need to convince the public.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "AdFrEx.North Santiva will remain untouched by criminal activity.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "AdAnEx.I’ve followed their every move. The public needs to know that the Guild can not move without us knowing about it.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "AdAnOp.No more shootouts, no more public car chases, all the danger is behind us.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "AdAnOp.Take this seriously, 1Hero. There are fifteen civilians now dead because of Guild violence.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "AdAnDe.The cost of their crimes is not merely financial.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "AdBaEx.Just remember, 1Hero: Over 300 arrests and most isolated in the south.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McBaEx.Madalyn is also here, and I have reason to believe that Charles Wilkes was a Guild leader too.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "AdAnOp.You need to stay out of this case, 1Hero.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McWoEx.But, Miss Kimura, Charles’ daughter could be in danger.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McWoEx.If something happens here in North Santiva after we’ve told the public that it’s safe, we’ll look bad.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "AdWoOp.Shit. I need to get to the Channel 4 skyrise soon.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "AdBaEx.I’ll be there with you this first time. But after today, you’ll be taking these interviews by yourself.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "AdBaEx.The interview starts in two hours. Security will meet you in the lobby.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McBaDe.This vase is made of metal. I’m not strong enough to break it open.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McBaDe.I have a rigging cable. Perhaps I can attach this hook and make a grapple.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "ErSaCl.I’m sorry, 1Hero. It was hot in the moment, but now…");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "ErWoOp.Are you kidding me? She’s going to fire you.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McBaEx.I have the commissioner on my side.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McSaEx.I’ll explain everything later. For now, I need to talk to Melissa.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McAnDe^.Shit! Maybe I can blame it on that fake virus.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McSaOp^.What have I gotten myself into now?");
